    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PRESENTATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Odessa features inventive characters, great dialogues and one of Indinera's best, most intriguing storylines - with a lot of thrilling twists and turns that will keep you thinking and guessing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retired bodyguard has to team up with a smart down-to-earth bunny-girl, an elegant but tight-lipped beggar and a stray dog to keep the hope of rescuing his soon-to-be wife, spectacularly abducted by mysterious, spine-chilling individuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the same time, a secretive cult around a strange goddess (the Goddess of Ashes) is developing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How could the two things be related? And will he be able to see his beloved one again?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play this exciting 2D RPG featuring both investigation and classic exploration, and find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 hours of playtime, 13 Relics, 8 Mystery Areas and 7 Animals to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45+ enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visible Enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autosave after each battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Options to customize your experience including Adjustable Battle Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Modes of Difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spells and skills you can master, to create even stronger &quot;super&quot; technics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Game +/++</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An enthralling plot full of twists and turns that will keep you guessing constantly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great dialogues featuring unique and well-developed characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantastic cut scenes to display better the intense plot twists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous weather effects for a more immersive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dreams! Nightmares! Like in Laxius Force and Soul!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indinera's signature and vintage style for gameplay and story</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
